{"id":38066,"date":"2022-08-02T09:58:55","date_gmt":"2022-08-02T05:58:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=38066"},"modified":"2023-10-05T20:58:56","modified_gmt":"2023-10-05T16:58:56","slug":"profit-at-expense","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/08\/02\/profit-at-expense\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Explotation: Warning of profit at a Muslim&#8217;s expense"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Mustawrid reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Whoever eats so much as a morsel at the expense of a Muslim\u2019s reputation, then Allah will feed him the likes of it in Hell. Whoever clothes himself with a garment at the expense of a Muslim\u2019s reputation, then Allah will clothe him with the likes of it in Hell. Whoever stands in a position of repute and fame at the expense of a man, then Allah will make him stand in a position of dishonor and infamy on the Day of Resurrection.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4881<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan li ghayrihi<\/em> (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064d \u0645\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0644\u0650\u0645\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064b \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0637\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0645\u064f\