, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdul Malik ibn \u2018Umayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever employs a man among his loved ones or relatives, employing him for no other reason besides that, then he has betrayed Allah, His messenger, and the believers.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Fa\u0304ru\u0304q 740 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/shafiee-advice-private\/","url_meta":{"origin":38066,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Nasihah: Sincere advice is given in private, not public","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever admonishes his brother in private has been sincere to him and protected his reputation. Whoever admonishes him in public has humiliated him and betrayed him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 9\/140 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0632\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0638\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32194,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/16\/boycotts-unless-allah-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":38066,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Boycotts: Boycotter in Hell, unless Allah shows mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever boycotts his brother for more than three days, he is in the Hellfire unless the generosity of Allah reaches him.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 18\/315 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32367,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/kibr-habbatin-min-khardalin\/","url_meta":{"origin":38066,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Kibr: Allah throws down the arrogant in Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has the weight of a mustard seed of arrogance in his heart, Allah will throw him down on his face in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 7015 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"